data.description: Welcome to this 3 bed home that is conveniently located in the Briarcliffe section of Glenolden.  This end unit offers tons of  natural light,  Central Air ( 2023), ample sized bedrooms,  partially finished basement with a  half bath, a  designated laundry area,  basement access to rear private driveway parking.  Other added features are a front and side yard with a spacious front patio, which is perfect for cookouts and get-togethers.  Move-in ready and waiting for your personal touch.  The property is close to all area amenities, and major highways.  Schedule your private tour today.
